snippet.title: Guidus Zero Devlog#3 ~Zin the Arcane wizard~
snippet.description:
Zin is an Arcane wizard who should be familiar to Guidus players.
She has two specialties: the Arcane Blade and the Arcane Release.
For now, let’s check out the Arcane Release first!
